Hey I have trouble with a plugin im doing and I was wondering how I can adding a cool down. My plugin makes it so that when you right
click a sword it will shoot a fireball now I want it to have a 5 second cooldown because you can spawm it. Please I need help in figuring
this out. Here is what I have so far.

@EventHandler(priority = EventPriority.HIGH) // Added event priority and
	// event
	public void onPlayerThrowingEvent(PlayerInteractEvent event) { // added the
		// actual
		// event
		if (!event.getAction().equals(Action.RIGHT_CLICK_AIR) == !event.getAction().equals(Action.RIGHT_CLICK_BLOCK)) {
			return;
		} else {
			ItemStack item = event.getPlayer().getItemInHand();
			if (event.getAction().equals(Action.RIGHT_CLICK_AIR)
					|| event.getAction().equals(Action.RIGHT_CLICK_BLOCK)) {
				if (item.getType() != Material.DIAMOND_SWORD) {
					return;
				} else {
					if (item.getType() == Material.DIAMOND_SWORD) {
						event.getPlayer().launchProjectile(SmallFireball.class)
								.setVelocity(event.getPlayer().getLocation().getDirection().multiply(1));
					}
					
				}
			}
		}
	}
